{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"forSourceId"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"sourceId"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"features","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"text":"Feature","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Feature","preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"], "},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The identifier of the style source.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"sourceId"},{"name":"features","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of GeoJSON features to be added to the source."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An arbitrary string used to track the given GeoJSON data.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"dataId"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The add operation will be scheduled and applied on a GeoJSON serialization queue."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In order to capture events when actual data is drawn on the map please refer to Events API","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"and listen to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onSourceDataLoaded"},{"type":"text","text":" (optionally pass the "},